222
00:19:00,765 --> 00:19:04,895
<i>If the stowaway microbes should happen
to come in contact with liquid water...</i>

223
00:19:05,061 --> 00:19:08,110
<i>...they can revive and reproduce.</i>

224
00:19:08,272 --> 00:19:13,494
<i>This may be how life
